["decision","E5-S5-T3",1774438090,"3357fe85-aee5-4df7-8ae8-71ad11d4f75f",{"topic":"AcceptedRisk classification","choice":"accepted-risk = no source link AND CitationAcceptanceCount \u003e 0; issue still appears in Uncited","rationale":"An acceptance record is a deliberate risk decision, not a citation. The issue remains uncited (no source link) but is separately tracked as accepted risk so callers can distinguish gaps from conscious risk acceptance."}]
