["note","E5-S5-T10",1774470128,"3357fe85-aee5-4df7-8ae8-71ad11d4f75f",{"msg":"Emitted source-link ops for all 119 issues across E2/E3/CI/TC/E4/E5 families. Also fixed readManifestForValidate in internal/validate/validate.go to read the 'entries' format (sources.Manifest) instead of the old 'sources' array format - the bug was causing every source-link citation to fail with 'unknown source' error. Rebuilt trls binary. Final coverage: 119/119 cited. Remaining errors are missing acceptance fields on E5-S5-T10/T11/T12, not citation issues."}]
